Detailed Description

Typedef Documentation

typedef struct CSIStream_Cfg_t CSIStream_Cfg

CSI Stream Configuration.

The structure is used to hold all the relevant configuration which is used to execute the CSI Stream test

typedef struct CSIStream_MCB_t CSIStream_MCB

Stream Demo Master Control Block.

The structure is used to hold all the relevant information for the Stream Demo.

typedef struct CSIStream_Stats_t CSIStream_Stats

CSI Stream statistics.

The structure is used to hold the statistics information for the CSI Stream Test
